    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Desert Hide.</strong></em> You have a thick hide. When you aren&rsquo;t wearing armor, your AC is 12 + your Dexterity modifier. Additionally, your thick hide is naturally adapted to hot climates, as described in chapter 5 of the Dungeon Master&rsquo;s Guide. Lastly, you are able to go a number of days without water equal to 3 + twice your Constitution modifier before suffering exhaustion.</p>",
